{"title":"Vertical’s Helium Dropper Loses Weight for 60mm Drop at 281g","link":"https://bikerumor.com/vertical-helium-dropper-worlds-lightest-60mm-drop-281g/","date":1694686714000,"content":"<p><img width=\"1600\" height=\"1067\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/vertical-helium-60mm-dropper-seat-post-ineos-grenadiers-tom-pidcock-pauline-ferrand-prevot.jpg\" alt=\"vertical helium dropper seat post gen 2 worlds lightest\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/vertical-helium-60mm-dropper-seat-post-ineos-grenadiers-tom-pidcock-pauline-ferrand-prevot.jpg 1600w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/vertical-helium-60mm-dropper-seat-post-ineos-grenadiers-tom-pidcock-pauline-ferrand-prevot-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/vertical-helium-60mm-dropper-seat-post-ineos-grenadiers-tom-pidcock-pauline-ferrand-prevot-800x534.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/vertical-helium-60mm-dropper-seat-post-ineos-grenadiers-tom-pidcock-pauline-ferrand-prevot-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/vertical-helium-60mm-dropper-seat-post-ineos-grenadiers-tom-pidcock-pauline-ferrand-prevot-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/vertical-helium-60mm-dropper-seat-post-ineos-grenadiers-tom-pidcock-pauline-ferrand-prevot-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/vertical-helium-60mm-dropper-seat-post-ineos-grenadiers-tom-pidcock-pauline-ferrand-prevot-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></p>\n<p>Ride Vertical has shaved more grams off its short-travel dropper seat post that had already laid claim to accolade of the world’s lightest. The Vertical Helium now weighs a claimed 281 grams in its 30.9mm diameter with a 60mm drop. That’s 23 grams lighter than <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/vertical-helium-dropper-seat-post-worlds-lightest/\" target=\"_blank\">the original</a> that launched at the end of 2022.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In addition to the 60mm drop used by Tom Pidcock (<a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/tom-pidcocks-pinarello-dogma-xc-hardtail-pro-bike-check/\" target=\"_blank\">on his XCC Pinarello Dogma HT</a>) there is a 90mm drop option, too. Both lengths are available in 30.9mm and 31.6mm options. In conjunction with the update, Vertical announces the Ignitor remote, too. Here’s more. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tom-pidcock-2023-world-champion-xco-race-vertical-helium-dropper-post-pinarello-dogma-fs.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tom-pidcock-2023-world-champion-xco-race-vertical-helium-dropper-post-pinarello-dogma-fs-800x534.jpg\" alt srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tom-pidcock-2023-world-champion-xco-race-vertical-helium-dropper-post-pinarello-dogma-fs-800x534.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tom-pidcock-2023-world-champion-xco-race-vertical-helium-dropper-post-pinarello-dogma-fs-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tom-pidcock-2023-world-champion-xco-race-vertical-helium-dropper-post-pinarello-dogma-fs-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tom-pidcock-2023-world-champion-xco-race-vertical-helium-dropper-post-pinarello-dogma-fs-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tom-pidcock-2023-world-champion-xco-race-vertical-helium-dropper-post-pinarello-dogma-fs-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tom-pidcock-2023-world-champion-xco-race-vertical-helium-dropper-post-pinarello-dogma-fs-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/tom-pidcock-2023-world-champion-xco-race-vertical-helium-dropper-post-pinarello-dogma-fs.jpg 1600w\" /></a><figcaption>Your 2023 XCO World Champion, Tom Pidcock, making good use of the Vertical Helium Dropper in Glentress, Scotland. Credit: Ellie Lawton.</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Vertical Helium Dropper Seat Post</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>To reduce the weight of the world’s lightest dropper seat post further, the team at Ride Vertical, Ricard Bages and Jordi Vilares, focused on reducing the thickness of the dropper’s aluminum tube. The designers say the new shape avoids stress concentration at the most critical points of the post.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/vertical-helium-dropperpost-gen2-lighter-with-remote-command.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/vertical-helium-dropperpost-gen2-lighter-with-remote-command-800x534.jpg\" alt srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/vertical-helium-dropperpost-gen2-lighter-with-remote-command-800x534.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/vertical-helium-dropperpost-gen2-lighter-with-remote-command-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/vertical-helium-dropperpost-gen2-lighter-with-remote-command-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/vertical-helium-dropperpost-gen2-lighter-with-remote-command-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/vertical-helium-dropperpost-gen2-lighter-with-remote-command-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/vertical-helium-dropperpost-gen2-lighter-with-remote-command-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/vertical-helium-dropperpost-gen2-lighter-with-remote-command.jpg 1600w\" /></a><figcaption>Claimed weights below pertain to the post only. The new Vertical Dropper Remote, aptly named the Ignitor, weighs a claimed 24g.</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The unique two-position locking mechanism has been tweaked, also. Unlike other designs, the Helium does not make use of a grooved main tube for its lock mechanism. Instead, it houses an Independent Locking Cartridge that utilizes a set of concentrically-positioned tubes deep within the post. As the main tube does not need to accomodate grooves, it can be made thinner. This is one of the reasons this post is so lightweight. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/ricard-bages-piston-head-insertion-locking-tube-cartridge-assembly-vertical-helium-dropper-seat-post.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/ricard-bages-piston-head-insertion-locking-tube-cartridge-assembly-vertical-helium-dropper-seat-post-800x534.jpg\" alt=\"vertical helium dropper locking tube cartridge assemblt\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/ricard-bages-piston-head-insertion-locking-tube-cartridge-assembly-vertical-helium-dropper-seat-post-800x534.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/ricard-bages-piston-head-insertion-locking-tube-cartridge-assembly-vertical-helium-dropper-seat-post-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/ricard-bages-piston-head-insertion-locking-tube-cartridge-assembly-vertical-helium-dropper-seat-post-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/ricard-bages-piston-head-insertion-locking-tube-cartridge-assembly-vertical-helium-dropper-seat-post-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/ricard-bages-piston-head-insertion-locking-tube-cartridge-assembly-vertical-helium-dropper-seat-post-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/ricard-bages-piston-head-insertion-locking-tube-cartridge-assembly-vertical-helium-dropper-seat-post-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/ricard-bages-piston-head-insertion-locking-tube-cartridge-assembly-vertical-helium-dropper-seat-post.jpg 1600w\" /></a><figcaption>Internals of the Independent Locking Cartridge on the Vertical Helium Dropper</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The carbon fiber post helps, too. All of the other major parts are made from 7075 T6 aluminium, including the very neat-looking, heavily-machined clamp. Its hardware is 6Al-4V Titanium, and the bolt heads are tightened with the use of a Torx 25.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/pauline-ferrand-prevot-rides-world-championships-scotland-vertical-helium-dropper-post.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"600\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/pauline-ferrand-prevot-rides-world-championships-scotland-vertical-helium-dropper-post-800x600.jpg\" alt=\"pauline ferrand-prevot ride vertical helium dropper pinarello dogma\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/pauline-ferrand-prevot-rides-world-championships-scotland-vertical-helium-dropper-post-800x600.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/pauline-ferrand-prevot-rides-world-championships-scotland-vertical-helium-dropper-post-297x223.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/pauline-ferrand-prevot-rides-world-championships-scotland-vertical-helium-dropper-post-120x90.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/pauline-ferrand-prevot-rides-world-championships-scotland-vertical-helium-dropper-post-768x576.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/pauline-ferrand-prevot-rides-world-championships-scotland-vertical-helium-dropper-post-1536x1151.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/pauline-ferrand-prevot-rides-world-championships-scotland-vertical-helium-dropper-post.jpg 1600w\" /></a><figcaption>Pauline Ferrand-Prevot also took the Rainbow Stripes this year aboard her Pinarello Dogma Hardtail with the Vertical Dropper seat post installed.</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h4>Claimed Weights</h4>\n\n\n\n<figure><table><tbody><tr><td>Vertical Helium Dropper Post</td><td>⌀ 30.9mm</td><td>⌀ 31.6mm</td></tr><tr><td>S (320mm x 60mm)</td><td>281 g</td><td>291 g</td></tr><tr><td>M (350mm x 90mm)</td><td>296 g</td><td>309 g</td></tr><tr><td>L (380mm x 90mm)</td><td>309 g</td><td>320 g</td></tr><tr><td>XL (410mm x 90mm)</td><td>316 g</td><td>334 g</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/vertical-helium-dropper-seat-post-remote-ignitor-lightweight-cable-housing-800x534.jpg\" alt=\"vertical helium ignitor  remote with lightweight cable housing\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/vertical-helium-dropper-seat-post-remote-ignitor-lightweight-cable-housing-800x534.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/vertical-helium-dropper-seat-post-remote-ignitor-lightweight-cable-housing-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/vertical-helium-dropper-seat-post-remote-ignitor-lightweight-cable-housing-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/vertical-helium-dropper-seat-post-remote-ignitor-lightweight-cable-housing-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/vertical-helium-dropper-seat-post-remote-ignitor-lightweight-cable-housing-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/vertical-helium-dropper-seat-post-remote-ignitor-lightweight-cable-housing-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/vertical-helium-dropper-seat-post-remote-ignitor-lightweight-cable-housing.jpg 1600w\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The aluminum Ignitor dropper remote offers up two mounting positions, and is compatible with SRAM Matchmaker. The lever pivots about low-friction IGUS bushings for easy actuation. It comes with a very lightweight housing (21 grams per meter).</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Pricing &amp; Availability</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Pricing on the Vertical Helium Dropper is unchanged, still at 399 € in all configurations. The Ignitor remote retails at 49<strong> </strong>€. Both are available now direct from Ride Vertical.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://ridevertical.eu/en/\" target=\"_blank\">ridevertical.eu</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/vertical-helium-dropper-worlds-lightest-60mm-drop-281g/\">Vertical’s Helium Dropper Loses Weight for 60mm Drop at 281g</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Jessie-May Morgan","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"00bab1bf0c36569b0235bfc9e9d3a50ba5c6dfbd7175363fd937663e255dec60","category":"Cycling"}